Introduction\par
\pard\sl276\slmult1\b0\fs22\par
\pard\fi720\sl276\slmult1 I want to try a new way of writing. The new method is highly collaborative, and requires everyone\rquote s help. It must be very interesting, inspiring, yet earn absolutely nothing. It needs to be open, transparent, and store all revisions. It needs to be so fundamentally useful that being able to read and understand it will function simultaneously as everything from a toolkit for understanding the universe to a cure for depression.\par
